<p>Astronomer Maciej Winiarczyk manages to film the northern lights and 'night-shining' clouds in Scotland</p><br/><p style="clear:both" /><img width='1' height='1' src='http://feeds.theguardian.com/c/34708/f/663867/s/304ed767/sc/23/mf.gif' border='0'/><br clear='all'/><br/><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/sc/23/rc/1/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/sc/23/rc/1/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/sc/23/rc/2/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/sc/23/rc/2/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/sc/23/rc/3/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/sc/23/rc/3/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/a2.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/a2.img" border="0"/></a><img width="1" height="1" src="http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/174726118897/u/53/f/663867/c/34708/s/304ed767/a2t.img" border="0"/>
